2013-02-06  Werner Lemberg  <wl@gnu.org>

	[ttdebug] Remove options `-n' and `d'; add `-v' to show version.

	* src/ttdebug.c: Include `common.h'.
	(Panic): Renamed to...
	(Abort): This to avoid name clash.
