	cache.
	(gblender_use_channels): New function.
	(gblender_reset_key): Improve.
	(gblender_lookup, gblender_lookup_channel): Comment possible call to
	gblender_reset.
	Fix computation of `idx'.
	(gblender_reset_channel_key): Fix computation of `a' and `r'.

